Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.38,0:00:04.55,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道恐鸟吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.84,0:00:06.55,Default,,0,0,0,,和鸵鸟很像哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.09,0:00:08.38,Default,,0,0,0,,诶～
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.59,0:00:10.47,Default,,0,0,0,,作为灭绝的动物
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.47,0:00:12.55,Default,,0,0,0,,渡渡鸟也是很有名的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.97,0:00:14.89,Default,,0,0,0,,也有和猫咪长得很像的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.02,0:00:15.89,Default,,0,0,0,,诶～
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.98,0:00:17.85,Default,,0,0,0,,仙石君真博学
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.85,0:00:19.52,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.52,0:00:22.73,Default,,0,0,0,,对她对他的称呼太在意 以致无法集中精力了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.19,0:00:25.65,Default,,0,0,0,,堀同学与宫村君
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.73,0:00:27.86,Default,,0,0,0,,开始播放了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.86,0:00:28.78,Default,,0,0,0,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.78,0:00:31.24,Default,,0,0,0,,不是猫咪是狗狗吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.62,0:00:32.32,Default,,0,0,0,,仙石会长
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.32,0:00:32.66,Default,,0,0,0,,仙石会长
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.70,0:00:34.45,Default,,0,0,0,,那说的是幼鸟吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.00,0:00:44.96,Default,,0,0,0,,好 热
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.80,0:00:48.34,Default,,0,0,0,,哇 好热
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.42,0:00:49.47,Default,,0,0,0,,你穿太多了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.97,0:00:51.89,Default,,0,0,0,,堀同学
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.60,0:00:53.80,Default,,0,0,0,,你在干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.26,0:00:56.14,Default,,0,0,0,,在等石川同学
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.23,0:00:59.27,Default,,0,0,0,,在这里等？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.27,0:01:00.98,Default,,0,0,0,,在教室等着不就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.02,0:01:02.90,Default,,0,0,0,,教室里开始扫除了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.77,0:01:05.65,Default,,0,0,0,,真拿你没办法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.90,0:01:08.07,Default,,0,0,0,,给你冰淇淋
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.86,0:01:10.40,Default,,0,0,0,,和透一起吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.03,0:01:11.91,Default,,0,0,0,,可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.03,0:01:13.62,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 多少钱
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.70,0:01:15.95,Default,,0,0,0,,不用啦 刚好半价时买的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.91,0:01:19.75,Default,,0,0,0,,平常总是你带蛋糕来我家 也挺不好意思的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.62,0:01:21.58,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.29,0:01:25.42,Default,,0,0,0,,至少在阴凉的地方等哦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.26,0:01:32.84,Default,,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.89,0:01:34.59,Default,,0,0,0,,是堀买来的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.85,0:01:35.99,Default,,0,0,0,,堀买的啊～
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.99,0:01:36.74,Note,,0,0,0,,{\alpha&H40&\fnResource Han Rounded CN Heavy\fs40\fscx100\bord0.5\frz11.22\frx6\fry352\move(345.645,179.473,467.867,51)}夕张\N蜜瓜
